### Sending Notifications

#### Campaign Approval Request
```json
{
    "tool": "contact_management",
    "action": "notify",
    "contact_id": "contact_12345",
    "message": "Requesting approval for Q4 lead generation campaign. Budget: $15K, Target: 1,000 qualified leads. Campaign details attached.",
    "channel": "email",
    "urgency": "normal"
}
```

#### Urgent System Alert
```json
{
    "tool": "contact_management",
    "action": "notify", 
    "contact_id": "contact_67890",
    "message": "Critical: Lead generation system experiencing 50% drop in performance. Immediate technical review needed.",
    "channel": "slack",
    "urgency": "critical"
}
```

